data.description: **Must See**Big Price Reduction**NEW CONSTRUCTION**This SINGLE LEVEL, two-bedroom + office space, 1,755 Sf' detached residence recently experienced an amazing transformation, and the result is stunning! An all-encompassing remodel project undertaken for an owner-occupant is now available to a truly fortunate buyer. This new homeowner will occupy one of the BEST VIEW LOTS in the Rancho Carlsbad community. You own the land on which this residence is situated, and THE VIEWS ARE REMARKABLE! The BRAND-NEW WINDOWS will infuse a daily sense of peace, tranquility, & gratitude. Rancho Carlsbad Estates is a wonderfully active 55+ neighborhood where. This friendly & safety conscious community offers golf, swimming, tennis, pickleball, exercise classes & workout facilities, in addition to community clubs & events. The 24-hour gated entry is professionally managed by attentive, friendly guards. Additional staff, assisted by roving golf cart personnel, play an integral part in looking out for residents while overseeing the upkeep of the beautiful common grounds. No speeding cars rushing by you in this community upsetting the peace & tranquility of your day, or your nighttime stroll around the neighborhood. You can lock & leave your home with confidence, as you take your time traveling the USA in the RV you store in RC’s storage facility. Be sure to view the photo gallery & take this home’s wonderful virtual tour, then come to see your next "home sweet home."
